The rare blue crystal mines turned the desert into a treasure trove for nobles, but they also became the final resting place for countless enslaved desert inhabitants.""

Yet their ancestral dwellings have crumbled to ruin, and the elders who have passed sealed away this history, burying unspeakable secrets of the past.""

Though frost has replaced the desert sands, the weapon marks carved into the surrounding cliffs remain as eternal scars.""
